      • additionalGlobalStatisticsPrettyNames

        protected java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.lang.String> additionalGlobalStatisticsPrettyNames
        OPTIONALLY Injected a map of additional migration statistics you'd like to track for a given migration, prop names to pretty names. i.e: "totalPagesRenditioned" -> "Total Pages Renditioned During this batch: "

      • additionalGlobalStatisticsValues

        protected java.util.Map<java.lang.String,java.util.concurrent.atomic.AtomicInteger> additionalGlobalStatisticsValues
        a map of migration statistic names to their values. You should not inject this - If you provide an additionalGlobalStatisticsPrettyNames variable, this map will be automatically initalized.
